data.name: label2.Text
data.value:
-If you are starting your journey from India to fly to Europe, your ticket purchased on ​StarkTickets will automatically be booked with an extra piece of baggage. So instead of one check-in piece in economy class, you would be entitled to two pieces of standard check-in baggage weighing not more than 23 kgs each.
-An upfront discount of up to EUR 50 equivalent in all booking classes for your travel to Europe.
-Rebooking is free of cost. Any difference in fare & taxes will apply.
Please use your university email-id at the time of making the booking and not a generic email ID. If your email address is not identified by StarkTickets, you may write to customersupport.@starktickets.com
Student documents (Student Visa, University Admission papers, etc.) must be presented at the time of check-in for verification.
-The extra bag should not weigh more than 23 kg with a maximum dimension of 158 cm -This offer is not combinable with any other baggage offer. -The offer does not apply to Economy Class tickets which already includes 2 pieces of check-in baggage allowance to Europe. -This offer is valid for tickets purchased on ​StarkTickets website
